Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:44.31,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}如伊卡洛斯一般
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.59,0:08:48.94,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}那份纯真的勇气如今已不在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.99,0:08:51.29,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}我们活着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.39,0:08:54.66,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}将那平凡的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:56.70,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}平凡无奇地度过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.71,0:09:01.36,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}怀着无数问号
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.45,0:09:09.18,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}寻找答案 却陷入迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.23,0:09:16.58,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}若能得知 答案的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.63,0:09:23.15,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}一切将化作崭新的音色
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.21,0:09:25.70,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}这阵风的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.74,0:09:31.39,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}定会有真实的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.47,0:09:33.30,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.37,0:09:35.91,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}这些泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.98,0:09:39.50,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}总有一天会干涸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.51,0:09:45.60,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}即使现在还很困难
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:50.74,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}即使现在还很遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:54.79,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}只需微微一笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.80,0:09:57.50,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}便能迎着清风 乱了呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.54,0:10:01.49,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)\be1}勇往直前吧
