Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.25,0:22:33.50,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}当两人漂移不定的心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.58,0:22:35.45,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}相互触碰之时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.59,0:22:42.38,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}此刻 你在想着谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.72,0:22:48.11,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}隔着玻璃晃过的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.15,0:22:50.01,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}那忧伤的侧脸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.14,0:22:56.35,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}距离那么近 却无法触及
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.53,0:23:00.82,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}积累种种借口
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.97,0:23:03.67,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}逃避着现在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.78,0:23:11.69,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}那时几近崩溃的软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.86,0:23:15.04,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}此刻仿佛已能面对
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.17,0:23:16.72,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}Love in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.76,0:23:19.15,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}打开门扉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.27,0:23:22.63,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}前往有你的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.77,0:23:29.70,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}告诉你这份焦灼已久的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.80,0:23:31.38,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}Feel my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.46,0:23:37.30,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}在你坦然露出笑容的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.39,0:23:40.85,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.91,0:23:44.65,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}会让我的泪水更坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.75,0:23:50.05,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}You are my only shooting star
