Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.81,0:00:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻 世界上只有我们两人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.17,0:00:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,0)}（前一天）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.67,0:00:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,0)}（放学后）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.65,0:00:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.87,0:00:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果汁也喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.80,0:00:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.32,0:00:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 学园长？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.77,0:00:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我们的顾问
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.49,0:00:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园长当顾问？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.59,0:00:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的业余爱好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.65,0:00:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是津名志拓人同学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.94,0:00:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.21,0:00:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于招到期待已久的新社员了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.06,0:00:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人都是从中等部时起就入社的老社员了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.87,0:01:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个社团很没人气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.37,0:01:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正相反
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.13,0:01:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太有人气所以抬高了门槛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.98,0:01:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心喜欢须方或者和子的人太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.09,0:01:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而不敢入社 怕成为众矢之的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.53,0:01:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 倒有不少准社员给我们做服装和舞台装置的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.15,0:01:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人同学也是冲着和子大人来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.67,0:01:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子大人是少爷的未婚妻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.25,0:01:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能随便说这种话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.80,0:01:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别叫我大人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.79,0:01:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有少爷也是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.27,0:01:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷就是少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.32,0:01:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子大人也是皆水大人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许婚的事也是我父母擅自决定的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.74,0:01:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 总之
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.28,0:01:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说中的美少年组合都到齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.24,0:01:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的「夜间飞行」剧团坚如磐石啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.86,0:02:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会设计一个能够最大限度发挥两人魅力的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人的魅力？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.93,0:02:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,0)}（和子妄想中）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.29,0:02:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在谁也看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.47,0:02:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 须方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.64,0:02:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天之前是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.00,0:02:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.72,0:02:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.14,0:02:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个妄想十分Good
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,100)}（你怎么知道的）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.06,0:02:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时没那方面企划
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.20,0:02:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,0)}（你们怎么知道的）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.16,0:02:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 剧本里也会加入和子的歌的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.55,0:02:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.83,0:02:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子的梦想是当歌手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.70,0:02:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是小时候的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.31,0:02:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年有泳装女优来这个岛上拍照时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.19,0:02:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有星探看中她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.57,0:02:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就别提啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子的歌声一听就会让人着迷的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.01,0:02:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 别说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.78,0:02:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺负人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.16,0:02:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用隐瞒的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.20,0:03:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必感到害羞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦想的确是越具体越容易实现的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对大家的将来都抱有很大的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.10,0:03:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜甜的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.08,0:03:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫糖汁？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.59,0:03:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 姿目·Tiger同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.93,0:03:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很香吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.96,0:03:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要来我们社看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.67,0:03:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗅觉与记忆有很深的关联
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.23,0:03:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种香味会刺激快乐的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.88,0:03:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你有没有想起什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有想起什么快乐的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快乐的…事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.16,0:04:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.79,0:04:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.12,0:04:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tiger回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你的银河里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.53,0:04:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉眠着怎样的绮罗星呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用老虎黄油烤的热饼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老虎黄油的热饼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.54,0:04:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在看画册
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.04,0:04:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个午后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和须方少爷并排坐着看那本画册
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.57,0:04:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 老虎黄油烤的热饼好像很好吃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:05:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷也说 是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那让你很开心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的笑容好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.48,0:05:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.42,0:05:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.90,0:05:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.95,0:05:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷是皆水大人的未婚夫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.74,0:05:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.29,0:05:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果皆水巫女和拓人同学凑成双
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.08,0:05:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方少爷就自由了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能错过机会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女心想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.66,0:05:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都要打倒乌贼大王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获得驶向银河世界的船只
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是萨姆开始用手中的鱼叉练习刺乌贼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.44,0:05:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了和乌贼大王作战的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.40,0:05:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 嘿 嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:05:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未经努力获得的胜利索然无味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌贼刺杀者萨姆的大名很快传遍全国
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌贼刺杀者萨姆…真有型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.91,0:06:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女一直在海边的小屋等待着萨姆的归来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 两人就同居了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.65,0:06:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.41,0:06:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是花季的少男少女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.58,0:06:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼星球好开放啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.72,0:06:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随之而来 两人有了共同的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.80,0:06:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶 我进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.28,0:06:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 奶奶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上哪儿去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.25,0:06:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是扬卷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.49,0:06:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我奶奶来过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.25,0:07:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店里的菠萝包我可全吃了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好吃啊 「南原」的菠萝包
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.40,0:07:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我要坐车
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.91,0:07:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.09,0:07:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人都不接
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.21,0:07:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.61,0:07:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.18,0:08:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,街上一个人都没
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是好在有你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.37,0:10:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之不是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.29,0:10:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.04,0:10:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.64,0:10:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我漂到岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.89,0:10:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你救的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.57,0:10:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.98,0:11:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是哪里都打不通
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.38,0:11:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淋湿了 换身衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.77,0:11:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座岛上没人的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.77,0:11:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去本土看看？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.94,0:11:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.03,0:11:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里不舒服？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.17,0:11:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从没离开过这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.84,0:11:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巫女有封印在身 就离不开岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.91,0:11:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说这是巫女的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要想离开岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.27,0:12:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非封印被破
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.07,0:12:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 一旦封印被破
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.97,0:12:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙的素体也会跑到岛外
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.87,0:12:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.37,0:12:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些话是谁告诉你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原先关于巫女的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是进入中学后 让奶奶教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.05,0:12:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我小学时 自作主张用了驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.22,0:12:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巫女使用驯化后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.54,0:12:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会共享得到素体的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.51,0:12:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成明白许多事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.96,0:12:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 上东京当歌手是根本不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.65,0:12:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.75,0:12:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当初可没少哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.02,0:13:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的变成只有我们俩的世界了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.99,0:13:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it's a pinch 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.52,0:13:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像看到个孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.82,0:13:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,图腾？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.84,0:13:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我认识…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.77,0:13:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我立的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.41,0:13:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候和须方他们一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.37,0:13:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是它…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几年前刮台风时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.90,0:13:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里发生塌方 应该不见了才对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.76,0:13:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.76,0:13:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么又会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:14:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里可能不是现实世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零时空间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.25,0:14:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是零时空间？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.23,0:14:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.14,0:14:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.54,0:14:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驯化！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么搞的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.85,0:14:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tauburn不来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.33,0:14:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说不是零时空间…吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.04,0:14:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人 真的好无忧无虑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.95,0:14:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.36,0:14:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从前就一直这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.73,0:14:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无忧无虑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到过去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.37,0:15:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口有这道印记之前的我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.87,0:15:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比现在封闭得多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.50,0:15:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 因为有以前的拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.59,0:15:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才有现在的拓人对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这乐观的想法很时髦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.88,0:15:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意对口喝的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.68,0:15:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驯化巫女素体的那个夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.10,0:15:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭了个够
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.25,0:15:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.12,0:15:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半夜肚子饿时入口的美味饭菜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我忽然想到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.22,0:15:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界不是只为折磨我而存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.91,0:15:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在想来也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.73,0:15:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有拓人这样的人出现在岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.57,0:15:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.02,0:15:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会动心的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.79,0:16:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种处境偶尔也不赖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.83,0:16:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人独处时才能谈的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.72,0:16:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏在这里面的回忆之类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.10,0:16:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回忆？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.72,0:16:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.31,0:16:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有能够创造风景的素体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台素体会根据闯入者的回忆和愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.65,0:16:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,编织出架空的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.71,0:16:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回忆和愿望？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太心软了 沉醉（Ivrogne）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是击败银河美少年的良机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.54,0:16:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成 想让她战斗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.50,0:16:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 看呐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.67,0:16:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人想妨碍你的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.71,0:17:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的愿望和回忆…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.47,0:17:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这雾是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,素体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.62,0:17:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.10,0:17:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人 得快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.98,0:17:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么认为？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.65,0:17:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台素体是幻像？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.85,0:17:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.70,0:17:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巫女应该能分辨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.46,0:17:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我和子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 那台素体是真实的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.06,0:17:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之说明这里是零时空间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.23,0:17:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则 素体不可能行动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:18:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是说 Tauburn也在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.08,0:18:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台素体如果有创造风景的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.72,0:18:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能藏起我的Tauburn
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.71,0:18:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会错 Tauburn就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷也常说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.73,0:18:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最珍贵的东西往往最难被察觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tauburn就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.78,0:18:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别松手 和子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.05,0:18:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驯化！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.18,0:19:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飒爽登场
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.34,0:19:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.12,0:19:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tauburn
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.79,0:19:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.55,0:19:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.93,0:19:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非…创造出这世界的愿望是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.89,0:19:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你独处的这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:19:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许源自我的愿望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她无法用素体战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.25,0:20:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是个恋爱的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.49,0:20:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先暂且不论
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.22,0:20:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次你的作战似乎成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.73,0:20:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保健室
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.27,0:20:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉怎么样 姿目同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.46,0:20:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.77,0:20:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是贫血
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.39,0:20:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说话途中突然晕倒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.57,0:21:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.84,0:21:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.41,0:21:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.08,0:21:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌贼刺客大人和少女有了怎样的秘密？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.28,0:21:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们吃了乌贼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.51,0:21:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在鱼星球上 乌贼是恶魔的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不可食用的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.04,0:21:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人却一起品尝了乌贼
